89.
224Nasanidassanaṃ nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sanidassano sanidassanasappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā ekaṃ, adhipatiyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.
